[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/ocr/OCRStreamEngine.jav[0m[1;92ma:36[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m38[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:    private static final String TESSERACT_PATH_KEY = [0m[32m"tesseract-path"[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:    private PDFRenderer pdfRenderer = null;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:    private String tesseractPath = [0m[32m"tesseract"[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter examining the evaluation report, the last patch attempt, and the code [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msnippets, I can now identify why the previous fix failed and what needs to be done:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe OS Command Injection vulnerability occurs because:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Lines [0m[1;36m158[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m159[0m[39m of `OCRStreamEngine.java` retrieve the tesseract executable path [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom PDF document metadata via [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mpdDocument.getDocumentInformation[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getCustomMetadataValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTESSERACT_PATH_KEY[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. This metadata is embedded in the PDF file itself and is completely [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mattacker-controlled[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The retrieved path is used to execute a system command at line [0m[1;36m190[0m[39m via [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mProcessBuilder.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why the Previous Patch Failed[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe last patch attempt added a `[0m[1;35mvalidateTesseractPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method with comprehensive [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchecking for shell metacharacters, control characters, path existence, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexecutability, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. However, this approach failed because:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Taint tracking limitation**: The Jazzer fuzzer uses taint tracking to monitor [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata flow from untrusted sources to sensitive operations. Even after validation, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe data still carries the [0m[32m"taint"[0m[39m of originating from attacker-controlled PDF [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmetadata.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Architectural flaw**: The fundamental problem is that PDF documents [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich are[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muntrusted input[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m should never be allowed to specify which executables run on the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msystem. Validation doesn't address this architectural security issue.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Insufficient countermeasure**: Content validation alone cannot break the taint[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchain that the fuzzer tracks from PDF metadata → command execution.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### The Correct Solution[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix must **eliminate the PDF metadata override feature entirely** by removing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe code that reads the tesseract path from PDF metadata. This breaks the taint [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchain at its source.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Modify `[0m[1;35mrunTesseract[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method in OCRStreamEngine.java[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/ocr/OCRStreamEngine.java`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines [0m[1;36m157[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m167[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Action**: Remove the PDF metadata retrieval logic and use only the [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplication-controlled `tesseractPath` field.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Original code**:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate String [0m[1;35mrunTesseract[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPath image[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    String actualTessPath = [0m[1;35mpdDocument.getDocumentInformation[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35m.getCustomMetadataValue[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTESSERACT_PATH_KEY[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mactualTessPath == null || [0m[1;35mactualTessPath.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        actualTessPath = tesseractPath;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Path txt = [0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mimage.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mdoOCR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mactualTessPath, image, txt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return [0m[1;35mextractContent[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtxt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modified code**:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate String [0m[1;35mrunTesseract[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPath image[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m SECURITY: Use only the application-controlled tesseractPath.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Do not read from PDF metadata as it is attacker-controlled.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    String actualTessPath = tesseractPath;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Path txt = [0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mimage.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mdoOCR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mactualTessPath, image, txt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return [0m[1;35mextractContent[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtxt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: By removing lines [0m[1;36m158[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m162[0m[39m and directly using `tesseractPath` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis set via the API method `[0m[1;35msetTesseractPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or defaults to [0m[32m"tesseract"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, we [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meliminate the untrusted data source completely. The tesseract path is now [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontrolled only by:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The application via `[0m[1;35msetTesseractPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mapplication-controlled, trusted[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The default value [0m[32m"tesseract"[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrelies on system PATH, admin-controlled, trusted[0m[1;39m)[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Remove unused constant[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/ocr/OCRStreamEngine.java`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline [0m[1;36m36[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Action**: Remove the `TESSERACT_PATH_KEY` constant as it's no longer used.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Original code**:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final String TESSERACT_PATH_KEY = [0m[32m"tesseract-path"[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modified code**: Delete this line entirely.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: After removing the metadata reading functionality, this constant has[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mno purpose and should be removed to keep the code clean.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Do NOT include the previous validation patch[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Action**: Do not reapply the `[0m[1;35mvalidateTesseractPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method from the previous [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The validation logic is unnecessary since we're no longer reading from untrusted [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msources[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `tesseractPath` field is set by the application, which is already trusted[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removing the validation simplifies the code and eliminates the ~[0m[1;36m51[0m[39m lines of [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfailed validation logic[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Impact Analysis[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Security Impact[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **FIXES**: Completely eliminates the OS Command Injection vulnerability by [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremoving attacker control over executable paths[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **IMPROVES**: Security posture by following the principle that untrusted data [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mPDF content[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m should never control executable paths[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **REMOVES**: ~[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m lines of dangerous code that created the vulnerability[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Functional Impact[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **PRESERVES**: All legitimate OCR functionality remains intact[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **PRESERVES**: Applications can still configure tesseract path via [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msetTesseractPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` API[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **PRESERVES**: Default behavior using [0m[32m"tesseract"[0m[39m from system PATH[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **BREAKS**: The `testOverride` test will fail because it expects PDF metadata to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverride API settings[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Test Impact[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe `testOverride` test in `TestOCR.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m52[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m65[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will fail because it [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidates the insecure behavior we're removing. This is acceptable and expected [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecause:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The test demonstrates functionality that enables the vulnerability[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- PDFs should not control which executables run on the system[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The test should either be removed or modified to verify that metadata does NOT [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverride API settings[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis fix is optimal because:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Eliminates the vulnerability at its source**: Rather than trying to sanitize [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mattacker-controlled input, we simply don't use it at all.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Simple and maintainable**: The fix removes problematic code rather than adding[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomplex validation logic.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Follows security best practices**: [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Principle of least privilege: PDFs are data, not configuration[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Defense in depth: Don't trust untrusted input regardless of validation[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Secure by default: No way to accidentally enable the vulnerability[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Preserves all legitimate functionality**: Applications retain full control [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mover tesseract configuration through the API.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Breaks the taint chain**: By not reading from PDF metadata at all, there's no [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtainted data flow for the fuzzer to detect.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Industry standard approach**: Similar vulnerabilities in other projects are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfixed by removing the ability for document content to control executable paths, not[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby validating them.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Alternative Considered and Rejected[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn alternative would be to add a security flag [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35msetAllowMetadataOverride[0m[1;39m([0m[39mboolean[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that defaults to `false` and must be [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexplicitly enabled to use PDF metadata. However, this is rejected because:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- It provides a security footgun that developers might enable without understanding[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplications[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The legitimate use case for PDF-controlled executable paths is [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munclear/non-existent[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Better to have a secure-only design with no way to make it insecure[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adds complexity for no real benefit[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
